snippet.title: High on Life: High on Knife DLC - 9 Minutes of Exclusive Gameplay | Comic Con 2023
snippet.description:
Check out 9 minutes of brutal exclusive gameplay from High on Life's upcoming High on Knife DLC, showcasing chainsaw action and a new gun featuring a pinball effect. Watch as alien enemies meet their demise. High on Life, the sci-fi first-person shooter game from Squanch Games, is available now on Xbox Series X/S, Xbox One, PC, PlayStation 4, and PlayStation 5. The High on Knife DLC will be available in fall 2023.

#IGN #Gaming #SDCC
